Nollywood Actor, Charles Okocha, aka Igwe 2pac, yesterday survived a ghastly car accident on the 3rd mainland bridge, Lagos. He made this known on his verified Instagram handle. According to the vibrant actor, God saved him from the hands of death. READ MORE: Accident Claims 10 Lives On Lagos-Ibadan Expressway He wrote: “Thankful for life 🙏🙏🙏Was involved in a car accident on 3rd mainland bridge last night but GOD DID!!! We Asaaaaa still ❤️” 